This repository contains research code, manuscript text, figures, and derived
outputs for a working paper on Stack Overflow.

Some tables, figures, and processed files are derived from Stack Exchange data.
The underlying Stack Exchange content is distributed by Stack Exchange and the
Internet Archive under Stack Exchange's Creative Commons terms. Reuse of those
derived artifacts may require Stack Exchange attribution and compliance with
the source data license.

The MIT license in this repository applies to the author's original code and
text. It does not override third-party rights in Stack Exchange source data or
close derivatives of that data.
